Create a new dataframe called cum_users_totals, with user totals by hour and dayOfWeek

cum_user_totals = ga %>%
  select(hour, dayOfWeek, users)  %>%
  group_by(hour, dayOfWeek, users) %>%
  summarize(total_users = sum(users), .groups = 'keep')

  theme_gray() +
